list.name: BLACK-PORTAL
list.description: Tara's Super cracks open a dimensional portal! A shadowy version of Tara appears and attacks her enemies.
list.descriptionHtml: Tara's Super cracks open a dimensional portal! A shadowy version of Tara appears and attacks her enemies.

list.name: HEALING-SHADE
list.description: Tara's Super cracks open a dimensional portal! A shadowy version of Tara appears to heal Tara and her teammates.
